    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="6" colcount="2" style="cell-padding:3px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Follower Shapes</text><text style="font-weight:normal;"> (See</text> also <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Cam-Follower-Motion" styleclass="Popup Box2">Cam-Follower Motions</link>)</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Follower</text> is the shape that is in continuous contact with the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">In <text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="font-size:10pt;">MechDesigner</text>, a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Follower</text> is a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Sketch-Loop" styleclass="Popup Box2">sketch-loop</link> with a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Profile-Element" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Profile</link> and <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Extrusion</text>.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
