        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2">2: Flat-faced Follower </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Four <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Lines</text> joined as a Long Rectangle</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Rectangle</text> must be long enough so that it is always in contact with the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
