        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2">4: Knife-Edged Cam-Follower</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="VariableName-small">very small </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">arc</text>, with other sketch-elements.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The small <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Arc</text> represent the knife-edge. </para>
